Package cps.server.controllers

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CarTransportationController
    Is used to make it possible to swap out different insertion/retrieval algorithms.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CarTransportationControllerA
    Implementation of a car insertion/retrieval algorithm.
    ComplaintController
    Handles requests that deal with customer complaints.
    LotController
    Handles requests that deal with Parking Lots.
    OnetimeParkingController
    Handles requests that deal with One-time Parking Services: - Incidental Parking (Park now) - Reserved Parking (Order now and park later)
    ParkingEntryController
    Processes ParkingEntry requests - when the user has a reservation or a subscription and now they want to park.
    ParkingExitController
    Processes ParkingExit request - when the customer came back and they want to retrieve their car.
    ReportController
    The Class ReportController.
    RequestController
    Base class for controllers that process user requests.
    SubscriptionController
    Processes customer requests for purchasing a monthly subscription - full or regular.
    UserController
    Processes login requests.
